\begin_inset Formula $u_{kt}^{2}$
\end_inset

 around 
\begin_inset Formula $E[u_{kt}^{2}]$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\log u_{kt}^{2} & \approx\log E[u_{kt}^{2}]+\frac{1}{E[u_{kt}^{2}]}(u_{kt}^{2}-E[u_{kt}^{2}])\\
 & =\log E[u_{kt}^{2}]-1+\frac{1}{E[u_{kt}^{2}]}u_{kt}^{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E[u_{kt}^{2}]=e_{k}^{\prime}\Sigma_{u}e_{k}
\]

\end_inset

