\begin_inset Formula $y_{t}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}$
\end_inset

, and eigenvalues and eigenvectors of 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}$
\end_inset

:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
u_{kt} & =e_{k}^{\prime}(y_{t}-A_{1}y_{t-1})\\
 & =e_{k}^{\prime}y_{t}-e_{k}^{\prime}A_{1}y_{t-1}
\end{align*}

