d-\lambda_{2} & -d+\lambda_{1}
\end{array}\right)\left[\begin{array}{c}
\lambda_{1}\\
\lambda_{2}
\end{array}\right]=\left[\begin{array}{c}
c\\
d
\end{array}\right]\\
